  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Mechanism | Add Mechanism (Editor)</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_">What is a Mechanism?</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">A <text styleclass="VariableName-IT">Mechanism</text>, in the context of <text styleclass="T_Menu">Add Mechanism</text>, is a <text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Editor</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> and </text><text styleclass="Interface">tab</text><text styleclass="Body Text">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Use <text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Editors</text> to add <text styleclass="Element">Parts</text>, <text styleclass="Element">Joints</text>, <text styleclass="Element">Cams</text>, <text styleclass="Element">Gears</text>, <text styleclass="Element">Belts</text>, ... to design your machine. </para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:21px;"><image src="hmtoggle_arrow0.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Element" figurelistinclude="0"></image><tab /><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="hmtoggle_arrow0.gif" src-expanded="hmtoggle_arrow1.gif"><caption><![CDATA[IMPORTANT: Gravitational Force Vector]]></caption></toggle><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="hmtoggle_arrow0.gif" src-expanded="hmtoggle_arrow1.gif" styleclass="Body Text"><caption><![CDATA[ is vertically down through the ]]></caption></toggle><toggle type="dropdown" print-expanded="true" help-expanded="false" defaultstyle="false" src-collapsed="hmtoggle_arrow0.gif" src-expanded="hmtoggle_arrow1.gif"><caption><![CDATA[TOP Plane]]></caption></toggle></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:21px;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Table">Before you add the first <text styleclass="Element">Mechanism-Editor</text>, think about the orientation of the machine. </para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table">For example, if your machine has an indexing or rotating table that is horizontal, you should add the <text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Editor</text> for the table to the <text styleclass="Interface2">Top</text><text styleclass="Element"> Plane</text><text styleclass="Body Text">, or a </text><text styleclass="Element">Plane</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> parallel to the </text><text styleclass="Interface2">Top</text><text styleclass="Body Text">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Element">Plane</text><text styleclass="Body Text">.</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Add Mechanism-Editor</para>
